OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted boss promises       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fminute's silence for head  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ofsted inspectors will hold a minute's 
OL,6, silence for head teacher Ruth Perry    
OL,7, during training around mental health.  
OL,9,FMrs Perry, whose suicide was linked to 
OL,10,Fan inspection by the education         
OL,11,Fwatchdog, died on 8 January 2023.      
OL,13,FHer sister, Prof Julia Waters met      
OL,14,FOfsted head Sir Martyn Oliver earlier  
OL,15,Fto discuss reforms in the organisation.
OL,17,FDuring the meeting, Sir Martyn said    
OL,18,Finspectors would be asked to pause for 
OL,19,Freflection during training scheduled on
OL,20,Fthe anniversary of Mrs Perry's death.  
